metadata.label: Additional Notes
metadata.value: This collection is organized and subsequently digitized in series reflecting a table of contents bound with the collection. The Table of contents has also been digitized and is available on this site: Titulos Primordiales de Hacienda de San Estevan Tiripitio, 1562-1786, Table of Contents. This particular document is from Series I[Y]: Amparo de Posecion del Ranch Uamado Sr Pedro en Jurisdiccion de Ario año de 1737.
